{"tid":1172659,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中美貿易戰之際　美駐華大使訪西藏　四年來首次","createTime":"2019-05-26T14:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T00:32:03.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"44277969b802ce25064c59a302abbebaa38e5169","tid":1172659,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T14:48:57.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰之際　美駐華大使訪西藏　四年來首次<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/20647/%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%A7%90%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E5%B8%83%E8%98%AD%E6%96%AF%E5%A1%94%E5%BE%B7-20648/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E4%B9%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%BE%8E%E9%A7%90%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E8%A8%AA%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F-%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F20647%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2597%258F-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25A7%2590%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%2598%25AD%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%25A1%2594%25E5%25BE%25B7-20648%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E9%25A7%2590%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2597%258F-%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BE%2586%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18BTmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=635bf5f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/20647/%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%A7%90%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E5%B8%83%E8%98%AD%E6%96%AF%E5%A1%94%E5%BE%B7-20648/%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E4%B9%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E7%BE%8E%E9%A7%90%E8%8F%AF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E8%A8%AA%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F-%E5%9B%9B%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1</a><br />\n<br />\n《美國之音》周一報道，美國駐中國大使館發言人表示，美國駐華大使布蘭斯塔德本星期訪問西藏。報道稱，「這次美中進行貿易戰之際的訪問，將是2015年以來，美國駐中國大使第一次進入西藏」。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普去年12月簽署國會通過的《西藏旅行對等法》（The Reciprocal Access to Tibet Act），該法案禁止向實行限制外國人進入西藏政策的中國官員，發出進入美國的簽證。美國國務院表示，2011年5月至2015年7月，美國官員總共提出39項外交人員訪問西藏的要求，只有4項獲得批准。<br />\n<br />\n中國當時對美國通過《西藏旅行對等法》強烈譴責，外交部發言人華春瑩表示，中方堅決反對美方執意簽署《西藏旅行對等法》，指法案嚴重違反國際關係基本準則，粗暴干涉中國內政，向藏獨分子發出嚴重的錯誤訊號，對中美交流合作嚴重危害。她指，法案對中國的指責是罔顧事實，充滿偏見，中方對此決不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n關於今次美國駐華大使到西藏，美國大使館發言人發表聲明說：「這次訪問，是大使與當地領導人接觸、表達長期以來對那裏限制宗教自由以及西藏文化及語言保護的關注的機會。」布蘭斯塔德從5月19日到25日訪問青海以及與之相鄰的西藏地區。美國駐華大使館發言人說，訪問行程包括正式會談以及參訪宗教和文化場所。"},{"pid":"30ea91d5b8fc0e8d5513aa41d33ab7fb83d0fc1e","tid":1172659,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>指法案嚴重違反國際關係基本準則</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似成日講呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係咩準則"},{"pid":"d3fc380b6495a7e6a970dfc416f575ad3db69668","tid":1172659,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T21:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0414e9be3d14755432815dbafa1f4557bb9563","tid":1172659,"uid":52946,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T21:47:51.000Z","msg":"咁驚比人去西藏做咩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24700173e50e4cac5b10cd0299a27b620269e06","tid":1172659,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T21:50:15.000Z","msg":"幾時去埋新疆"},{"pid":"f3f86475e9ec4a442cbafcbc86d62479377df750","tid":1172659,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T00:21:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13eea79aa8d1783b420e5cc175079c4e62a8a9bd","tid":1172659,"uid":56123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30ea91d5b8fc0e8d5513aa41d33ab7fb83d0fc1e","tid":1172659,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>指法案嚴重違反國際關係基本準則</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似成日講呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /